2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a novel approach for domain generalisation using machine learning techniques such as deep neural networks. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper addresses a common problem in AI, which is the domain shift problem, and proposes a solution using AI techniques. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper uses deep neural networks as a key component of the proposed approach. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image datasets and proposes a method for generating new images, which falls under the domain of multimedia.
